ays in her book \u003cem\u003eJoie: A Parisian’s Guide to Celebrating the Good Life\u003c/em\u003e to pick one main focal point, like vibrant plateware, and stick to it.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n  \u003cfigure\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ca href=\"https://www.pinterest.com/pin/create/button\" data-pin-do=\"buttonPin\" data-pin-media=\"\" data-pin-custom=\"true\" data-ga-event=\"inPageInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"Pinterest Share\" data-ga-event-label=\"Article Body Image\" data-ga-destination-url=\"none\"\u003e\n        \u003csvg xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" viewBox=\"0 0 16.9 20.8\"\u003e\u003cpath d=\"M16.8 6.3C16.5 3.2 13.6.4 10.1.1 4.8-.5.1 2.7 0 7.9c0 2.4.8 4 2.9 4.8 1.5-1.5-.3-2.4-.5-4C2 4.3 7.1.1 11.7 2.9c3.2 1.9 2.6 9.9-1.2 10.7-.8.1-1.8-.1-2.1-.5-1.9-1.8 1.5-4.8.4-7.3-.9-2.1-3.6-.4-3.9 1.5-.2 1 .3 2 .3 2.9 0 2.1-1.3 5-1.7 7.1-.2.9-.3 2.6-.1 3.4h1.5c1-1.6 1.6-4.1 2.1-6.3.3-.2.5.4.7.6 1.8 1.4 5 .6 6.4-.7 2.1-1.7 3-5.2 2.7-8\" fill=\"currentColor\"\u003e\u003c/path\u003e\u003c/svg\u003e\n      \u003c/a\u003e\n\n      \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/yMLvI-KzGdvHtP4a0NNyj5I5HiE=/778x778/filters:format(webp)/d755a0db-3473-45ae-8822-b6a2be898ae4--image-3_opt_1.jpg, https://images.food52.com/KjjeLM5An64WilXQTEIn57lAi10=/1556x1556/filters:format(webp)/d755a0db-3473-45ae-8822-b6a2be898ae4--image-3_opt_1.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" media=\"(min-width: 1400px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/t78TheMZIlMcv387dmtpO4T9K2A=/778x778/d755a0db-3473-45ae-8822-b6a2be898ae4--image-3_opt_1.jpg, https://images.food52.com/-vCiRQP9b_Vmi_VXtOaAe8D0gn8=/1556x1556/d755a0db-3473-45ae-8822-b6a2be898ae4--image-3_opt_1.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base