.food52.com/GQqMvCVIJm0WspdEJpsKxvR_ll0=/1536x1918/15b13077-7c44-430d-b496-235fb233acb5--HED_1.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/KKZGUgHUPly50sAhyU1ukRhwrV4=/375x468/filters:format(webp)/15b13077-7c44-430d-b496-235fb233acb5--HED_1.jpg, https://images.food52.com/wN5lzsGfCLlnBT6OQtJ-f2aK91k=/750x936/filters:format(webp)/15b13077-7c44-430d-b496-235fb233acb5--HED_1.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/sKUCm1UUSIPwNegW4sdaRqph66Q=/375x468/15b13077-7c44-430d-b496-235fb233acb5--HED_1.jpg, https://images.food52.com/x5DtoUvQfwhzRmqRrc5M1ZJ5FZ8=/750x936/15b13077-7c44-430d-b496-235fb233acb5--HED_1.jpg 2x\" alt=\"\" width=\"964\" height=\"1204\" data-expand=\"750\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/sKUCm1UUSIPwNegW4sdaRqph66Q=/375x468/15b13077-7c44-430d-b496-235fb233acb5--HED_1.jpg, https://images.food52.com/x5DtoUvQfwhzRmqRrc5M1ZJ5FZ8=/750x936/15b13077-7c44-430d-b496-235fb233acb5--HED_1.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \u003c/figure\u003e\n\n              \n  \n\n\n\n              \u003ch2\u003e6. Slow and Steady\u003c/h2\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eMost importantly: Breathe. Slow down. Be present. When emulating \u003cem\u003ejoie de vivre\u003c/em\u003e, this is vital. Julia Child said, “No matter what happens in the kitchen, never apologize.” No one will remember a mishap, but they will remember how you made them feel. \u003cem\u003eBon courage!\u003c/em\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003e\u003ci\u003e*Maker\u0026#39;s Mark 46®️ Kentucky Straight Bourbon Whisky Barrel Finished with 10 French Oak Staves, 47% Alc./Vol. ©️2025 Maker\u0026#39;s Mark Distillery, Inc., Loretto, KY\u003c/i\u003e\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \n              \u003ccenter\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eHow are you hosting this summer? What are your best garden party tips?\u003c/em\u003e\n\u003c/center\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
